{"about_the_game":"Easy to pick up, and hard to put down! Parry Nightmare is a one-of-a-kind &quot;parry heaven&quot; action game where the best offense is a good defense!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/gif1_p.gif?t=1727154074\" /><br><br>Use your nightmare's strength against it with your trusty parry move! Stun foes, send away projectiles, and stop threats right in their tracks by chaining parries!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/gif2_p.gif?t=1727154074\" /><br><br>Honno-chan will defeat any foes you stun automatically. Leave them to her and focus on the defense!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/gif3_p.gif?t=1727154074\" /><br><br>Parrying grants your soul more and more courage to face the night! Heal up by continuing to parry! Spend excess soul to unleash a powerful Burst move to wipe out hordes of enemies at once!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/gif4_p.gif?t=1727154074\" /><br><br>Collect powerups from rare foes to supercharge Honno-chan! Breathe fire, deploy orbital pain, wreak havoc, and more!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/gif5_p.gif?t=1727154074\" /><br><br>Defeated enemies drop light. Collect light and the darkness of the nightmare abates, giving you a clearer view of the chaos. Max out your light meter to beat the nightmare!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/gif6_p.gif?t=1727154074\" /><br><br>Will you be able to escape the nightmare and greet a new day...?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/9.gif?t=1727154074\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Countless Tears Shed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/281dd83780d5d9257085690fe4bab80281cdc01b.jpg"},{"name":"Countless Cries of Pain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/5c4bc59813d37c548ad1d64230e3569f362f60e1.jpg"},{"name":"All is Forgotten","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/47f1677b85e4bd07fc1d86f9bba3fdb84a2d7d2e.jpg"},{"name":"As We Greet the Morning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/18c06e39b087d4ef42a2d4e80eb71e36537e21e0.jpg"},{"name":"A Sigh in the Dead of Night","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/4a406b9959a361c29adcc0c70c20984f87cb4e2d.jpg"},{"name":"Snug as a Bug in a Rug","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/fbdd0c0791ce347847f0a578e2604b98a6c92d5b.jpg"},{"name":"Together with the Dawn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/ea2a056b7f0b279a17ba018e3858b756a3b06a5e.jpg"},{"name":"Wipe it All Away","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/bae089422e669133317a6d3cffe2aea0eccd5566.jpg"},{"name":"Remove What's Left of the Nightmare","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/9b27faa303bd9c167c58cf3f4f0048134b294f11.jpg"},{"name":"Step into an Enchanting World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2081230/58957825a7c898c2c187497ab6cf2988992a31a1.jpg"}],"total":34},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727154074","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/page.bg.jpg?t=1727154074","capsule_image":"https://shared.a